import { TextInput,Pressable,Text,View } from "react-native"

export default function AddTodo(){
    return(
    <View>
        <View>
            <Text>Judul</Text>
            <TextInput></TextInput>
        </View>
        <View>
            <Text>Jam</Text>
            <TextInput></TextInput>
        </View>
        <View>
            <Text>Keterangan</Text>
            <TextInput></TextInput>
        </View>
        <Pressable>
            <Text>Add Todo</Text>
        </Pressable>
    </View>)
}
